highlights.text: “After LIKE” by IVE is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 55 spots at #48.
“Hold Me Closer” by Elton John and Britney Spears is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #25.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #3.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 291 weeks straight.
